trans-unit.source: The type of elements in the collection.
<c>C</c> must implement the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> interface.
Represents a generic collection of <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> objects.
An <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601> can be dynamically resized.
The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> to add to the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />.
Adds an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> to the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />.

To determine whether an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601> is read-only, call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 확인 하려면 여부는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601> 는 읽기 전용 호출에서 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> 메서드.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" /> is read-only.
Removes all elements from the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />.

To determine whether an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601> is read-only, call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 확인 하려면 여부는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601> 는 읽기 전용 호출에서 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> 메서드.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" /> is read-only.
The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> to locate in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />.
Returns a value that indicates whether the specified <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> is in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" />가 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />에 있는지 여부를 나타내는 값을 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> is in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" />가 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />에 있으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional array that is the destination of the elements copied from the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />.
The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: <c>배열</c>에서 복사를 시작할 인덱스입니다. 이 인덱스는 0부터 시작합니다.

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" /> to a compatible one-dimensional array, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: 대상 배열의 지정된 인덱스에서 시작하여 전체 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />을 호환되는 1차원 배열에 복사합니다.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is <see langword="null" />.
<paramref name="arrayIndex" /> is less than 0.
<paramref name="array" /> is multidimensional.
-or-

The number of elements in the source <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" /> is greater than the available space from <paramref name="arrayIndex" /> to the end of the destination array.
trans-unit.target: 소스 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />의 요소 수가 대상 배열의 <paramref name="arrayIndex" />부터 끝까지 사용 가능한 공간보다 큰 경우

trans-unit.source: -or-
Type <paramref name="C" /> cannot be cast automatically to the type of the destination array.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="C" /> 형식을 대상 배열의 형식으로 자동 캐스팅할 수 없는 경우

trans-unit.source: Returns the number of elements contained in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />.
The number of elements contained in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />.
Returns a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" /> is read-only.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />가 읽기 전용인지 여부를 나타내는 값을 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" /> is read-only; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" />가 읽기 전용이면 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> to remove from the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />.
Removes the first occurrence of a specific <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> from the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />.
<see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="item" /> is successfully removed; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="item" />이 제거되면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: This method also returns <see langword="false" /> if <paramref name="item" /> was not found in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드는 <see langword="false" />가 <paramref name="item" />에 없는 경우에도 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" />를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: To determine whether an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601> is read-only, call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 확인 하려면 여부는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601> 는 읽기 전용 호출에서 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> 메서드.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1" /> is read-only.
